    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in its current 'as-is' condition and will require significant attention. The engine is currently running rough, and there are noticeable leaks that need to be addressed. Body-wise, there is visible rust on the lower panels and several deep scratches and dents throughout. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project for someone mechanically inclined or as a source for parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
